You've completed an extraordinary journey. <break time="2s"/>
The Threshold has been crossed. <break time="2s"/>
And you have returned with gifts. <break time="3s"/>

In the hours and days ahead... pay attention to your dreams... to moments of insight... to synchronicities. <break time="3s"/>
The integration continues beyond this session. <break time="3s"/>

When you're ready... at your own pace... allow your eyes to open. <break time="4s"/>

Welcome back. <break time="2s"/>

You've journeyed far... and you've returned. <break time="2s"/>
You carry the threshold within you now... <break time="2s"/>
